  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/afb67d0d072f099877f98ead54965237.avif?t=1770782036\" width=256 height=128 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"Unable to navigate, probably on course\"</i></strong> was commonly found in ships' logs of 19th century naval vessels, left without accurate navigational guidance due to poor visibility. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this casual adventure story, U.N.P.O.C. describes a hotel employee's struggle to navigate his own happiness, desperate for financial freedom. Find clues, solve puzzles, and survive the opportunity to find a fortune lost at sea centuries ago. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Open World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your procedurally generated world and select up to 10 islands for a unique experience and challenge. Keep your survival grades high as you explore ship wrecks, find buried treasure, and sail from island to island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/e3adbf39482126853605fc6cc0cff5b4.poster.avif?t=1770782036\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/e3adbf39482126853605fc6cc0cff5b4.webm?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/e3adbf39482126853605fc6cc0cff5b4.mp4?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Treasures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sunken shipwrecks, buried chests, and hidden chambers are scattered throughout the world waiting to be discovered. Investigate them all to receive a perfect treasure hunting grade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/129a10a4bb2861aef29f8bc5ee912020.poster.avif?t=1770782036\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/129a10a4bb2861aef29f8bc5ee912020.webm?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/129a10a4bb2861aef29f8bc5ee912020.mp4?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various puzzles keep the adventure enticing. Find your way through an open ocean maze, crack a lost combination, and solve many other mental challenges while chasing 'Opportunity'.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/89d3479e0eb7ab9543923a7264a4bf11.poster.avif?t=1770782036\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/89d3479e0eb7ab9543923a7264a4bf11.webm?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/89d3479e0eb7ab9543923a7264a4bf11.mp4?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/afb67d0d072f099877f98ead54965237.avif?t=1770782036\" width=256 height=128 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"Unable to navigate, probably on course\"</i></strong> was commonly found in ships' logs of 19th century naval vessels, left without accurate navigational guidance due to poor visibility. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this casual adventure story, U.N.P.O.C. describes a hotel employee's struggle to navigate his own happiness, desperate for financial freedom. Find clues, solve puzzles, and survive the opportunity to find a fortune lost at sea centuries ago. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Open World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your procedurally generated world and select up to 10 islands for a unique experience and challenge. Keep your survival grades high as you explore ship wrecks, find buried treasure, and sail from island to island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/e3adbf39482126853605fc6cc0cff5b4.poster.avif?t=1770782036\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/e3adbf39482126853605fc6cc0cff5b4.webm?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/e3adbf39482126853605fc6cc0cff5b4.mp4?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Treasures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sunken shipwrecks, buried chests, and hidden chambers are scattered throughout the world waiting to be discovered. Investigate them all to receive a perfect treasure hunting grade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/129a10a4bb2861aef29f8bc5ee912020.poster.avif?t=1770782036\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/129a10a4bb2861aef29f8bc5ee912020.webm?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/129a10a4bb2861aef29f8bc5ee912020.mp4?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various puzzles keep the adventure enticing. Find your way through an open ocean maze, crack a lost combination, and solve many other mental challenges while chasing 'Opportunity'.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/89d3479e0eb7ab9543923a7264a4bf11.poster.avif?t=1770782036\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/89d3479e0eb7ab9543923a7264a4bf11.webm?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3528590/extras/89d3479e0eb7ab9543923a7264a4bf11.mp4?t=1770782036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
